headline: A Look At Ameriprise Financial (AMP) Valuation As Earnings Results Approach After Prior Revenue Beat
summary: Ameriprise Financial (AMP) is back in the spotlight ahead of its earnings report this Thursday morning, after previously beating revenue expectations by 3.8% and prompting interest in whether that momentum can hold. See our latest analysis for Ameriprise Financial. Ahead of earnings, Ameriprise Financial’s recent 4.1% 3 month share price return contrasts with a 1 year total shareholder return decline of 11.7%, while the 5 year total shareholder return of 162.3% points to stronger longer term...
